{"tid":668092,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔知有冇人記得我地呢?]UP圖網 - Imag.cx","createTime":"2018-05-17T10:11:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-22T04:46:44.000Z","uid":45332,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a23a4b2e26246c93d6b6bfa453e261c8f12d619d","tid":668092,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imag.cx/content/images/system/logo_1477128700606_d81471.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimag.cx%2Fcontent%2Fimages%2Fsystem%2Flogo_1477128700606_d81471.png&h=3c90501a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔經唔覺，<br />\n<a href=\"http://Imag.cx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FImag.cx&d=j%2Fc0ea5WgjbMERNZizTXtNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=e89d9e7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Imag.cx</a> UP圖網已經踏入第三個年頭<br />\n為左慶祝我地係冇任何廣告收入嘅情況下捱到三年都重未收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地對註冊用戶開放每張圖最大大小為80MB以答謝用戶長期嘅支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢可以一次upload多張圖片 <br />\n同時比哂咁多個IMG code比你 <br />\n又有相簿功能，剔返D相 <br />\n唔洗逐個CODE慢慢COPY<br />\n方便出POST放J圖既巴打 <br />\nBAM圖都OK <br />\n但係記得要SET做Private <br />\n每張圖最大80MB，我唔信你唔夠用 <br />\n歡迎各位巴絲開POST UP圖上黎 <br />\n<br />\n基於Google Adsense對圖片站嘅歧視<br />\n我地係冇廣告收入嘅<br />\n有能力既巴打可以贊助iMassGraphic <br />\n<a href=\"https://imag.cx/page/donate\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimag.cx%2Fpage%2Fdonate&d=j%2Fc0ea5WgjbMERNZizTXtNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=50bb123c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imag.cx/page/donate</a> <br />\n五蚊十蚊都對網站有唔小既支持架 <br />\n<br />\n本站強制用HTTPS <br />\n同時本站支援IPV6 <br />\n不過係香港家用上網市場 <br />\n應該得PCCW用到 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://imag.cx/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimag.cx%2F&d=j%2Fc0ea5WgjbMERNZizTXtNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=bfccd460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://imag.cx/</a>"},{"pid":"cf014881c29fb22a09935d05399a139ce122ef61","t